import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter, Route, Switch } from 'react-router-dom'
import StorePicker from './components/StorePicker'

const ReactRouter = () => (
  <BrowseRouter>
    <Switch>
      <Route exact path = '/' component={StorePicker} />
    </Switch>
  </BrowseRouter>
  )


export default ReactRouter
